item.title: Return of the Meme: 1523 (cog of a horror world)
item.description:
Let's... whatever.
Tried to go to bed early. Too stressed to sleep.
Stress-vomited.
Couldn't sleep with trying new mouthpiece because fuck it i might as well try new thing for desperate measures even though its not for apnea if it kills me it would be a bonus.
I know for an absolute FACT I missed the Northern lights last night, they were visible in Jerome, 7 miles away. But I wanted to be a good little submissive work slave so I stayed in bed, my brain screaming, until finally I passed out at midnight...
Four hours after I tried to get to bed early in the forst place, because I need to sleep as much as possible.
Woke up basically screaming in my brain, heart rate in panic mode.
Why is my body and brain like this?
It's literally just booking rich people into an overly fancy hotel. That's more or less all im doing. Why does it stress me out so much? Why can other people do it but I can't?
I am dry heaving so hard even Pippin is trying to imitate me.
I want to jump off a cliff.
I want to die. I want to die. Why cant I just die? Blugh.
Debating just fucking cutting and running but I have no insurance, no nothing at this moment so I cant get the help I need or go, uh, seaside to the grippy sock place. On top of that, nobody is around to care for Pippin other than me. Kayla is on vacation.
Whatever.
Yeah this is a fucking mood.
Maybe ive had too much caffeine in the last day but I have no choice because it keeps me from sleep at work.
Yeah. This is my brain today.
Pippin is trying frantically to preen my eyelashes.
OH and mom is in the hospital again with fuck knows what going on with her stomach (again) so yaaaay.
I was born in the wrong time. I may be lovable, but im not suited for this age.
I want to scream i cant scream i want to scream.
I am my own man-made horror, beyond my own comprehension, in the cog or a horror world.
I wish I didn't have a body with apnea. I wish I didn't have a body.
Perfect may be the enemy of good except in capitalism where perfect is not good enough.
Yeah thats about right. I need fo suffer better.
Yeah. This.
I honestly would probably join a monastery, I think id be a better fit for one--but I cant, because of student loan debt. It is a tie to the world that must be paid off in full before becoming a monk: it's Canon law.
Now i sit catatonic, screaming, wanting to sleep, wanting to stay awake, wanting to work, wanting to die, wanting to live. But also wanting to "want."
I dont know what to do. I have to get the doctor's note by Friday, was going to leave early today, maybe I just quit and go into the grippy sock place but the grippy sock place up here is pretty bad all accounts considered and I cant afford it and I cant afford it and I want to die and nobody is here to care for Pippin while I go.
Pippin tax. Today's message from Pippin: [nervous reep noises] ______ 1) Are you on the run to a safe place and passing through Arizona on your way to safer grounds? My apartment is open to you to crash at, and it is a safe space. Pippin and I will make you a meal and gladly share tea, wine, or mead with you. 2) Hey! Take your meds with a full glass of water, please. Do it for Pippin, or Space Mom, or better yet, do it for yourself. 3) Ĝefeloað wē. We will carry on. 4) all funds from the sales of items at these two links will be sent to support charities aiding to fight for Trans rights in the US (not just T-shirts!) https://www.teepublic.com/t-shirt/74812801-all-conures-are-anarchists https://www.teepublic.com/t-shirt/74811778-whiptail-pride 5) Since multiple people have requested this over the last two weeks or so, my ko-fi is: https://ko-fi.com/codyandpippin
